{"tid":960723,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好憎打邊爐？","createTime":"2018-12-29T15:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T02:42:54.000Z","uid":74090,"like":10,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cfcf373047fd002d995c8a7fca0c886e1d9283bf","tid":960723,"uid":74090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T15:41:05.000Z","msg":"咁多食法，最憎就係打邊爐，特別人多嘅時候，十幾樣又豬牛羊，又海鮮，又什菜放落一個煲入面撈埋一堆，咩湯底都變臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上成班人用個已撈到咁雜嘅湯底，煮乜出黎都有陣怪肉味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重要每人平都百幾蚊<br />\n真係寧願食個牛肉麵算，起碼有陣清香味道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXJ2D3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXJ2D3d.jpg&h=f20baa75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3eb9ebaacb817ce016c7d017c5f8efa8393901f","tid":960723,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fad829ac9a233ab8c8f41155613dd17380d03b","tid":960723,"uid":62815,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T15:58:33.000Z","msg":"好憎人落紫薯芋頭<br />\n一定搞到鍋湯唔知似乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28afcbfa3414d191b4b29297be31f2e7fe41ba6","tid":960723,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"任食打邊爐仲要一大班人share一個湯底=食屎<br />\n最理想係逐碟叫逐碟俾錢、人數最多4位，咁個湯底就唔會比大量垃圾質素嘅食物搞到一兜餿水咁<br />\n<br />\n其實我憎bbq多過打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9214a09141f3224f62d96d37904c1a5d9ac34008","tid":960723,"uid":216907,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"由細到大都唔識欣賞打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撈埋一埋野，烚熟就叫煮好<img src=\"/asse